fm: void reverseString(vector<char> &s) {     int i;     int n = s.size();     for (i = 0; i < n / 2; i++) {       int temp = s[i];       s[i] = s[n - i - 1];       s[n - i - 1] = temp;     }   }

fm: int distributeCandies(vector<int>& candyType) {     int n = candyType.size();     map<int, int> m;     for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {       m.insert({candyType[i], 1});     }     int maplen = m.size();     if (maplen >= n / 2)       return n / 2;     else       return maplen;   }

fm: int minAddToMakeValid(string s) {     int open = 0;     int close = 0;     stack<char> sta;     for (int i = 0; i < s.size(); i++) {       if (s[i] == '(') {         sta.push(s[i]);         open++;       } else if (sta.empty() == false and s[i] == ')' and sta.top() == '(') {         open--;         sta.pop();       } else {         sta.push(s[i]);         close++;       }     }     return close + open;   }
